; Coverage test for filters.cc lines 345-351
; Test POST_MUST_BALANCE flag with virtual postings.
; Balanced virtual posts use square brackets and set POST_MUST_BALANCE.
; This exercises the auto_virtualize check in handle_value.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food          $10.00
    [Budget:Food]         $-10.00
    [Budget:Savings]       $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal --subtotal
             $-10.00  Assets:Cash
                   0  Budget
             $-10.00    Food
              $10.00    Savings
              $10.00  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test
